    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen option `foldcolumn`  be set, delete the char  will delete the char before in the cmdline window.\r\n```lua\r\nvim.o.foldcolumn = \"1\"\r\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. nvim --clean\r\n2. :lua vim.o.foldcolumn = \"1\"\r\n3. type `<C-f>` to open the cmdline window\r\n4. delete a char in the cmdline window\n\n### Expected behavior\n\ndelete the char befor the cursor, not the char before the char.\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.10.0-dev-2008+g4ee656e4f\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno,  8.2.2121\n\n### Operating system/version\n\n5.15.133.1-microsoft-standard-WSL2\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nWezTerm 20230712-072601-f4abf8fd\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from repo",
